headline: Ingersoll Rand to Participate in Upcoming Investor Conference
summary: DAVIDSON, N.C., Nov. 19, 2024 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- Ingersoll Rand Inc., (NYSE: IR) a global provider of mission-critical flow creation and life science and industrial solutions, announced that Vik Kini, chief financial officer, will participate in a fireside chat at the Goldman Sachs Industrials and Materials Conference on Thursday, December 5, 2024, at 9:20 a.m. Eastern Time. A real-time audio webcast of the fireside chat can be accessed via the Events and Presentations section of the Ingersoll
